Package: virKra
Title: Exports viral reads classified by Kraken2 to a Seurat Object.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    c(
        person("Lidia", "Garrido-Sanz", email = "lgarrido@irsicaixa.es", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Javier", "Martinez-Picado", role = "ctb"),
        person("Sara", "Morón-López", email = "smoron@irsicaixa.es", role = "aut")
    )
Description: This package takes reads from single-cell 10x Chromium system that had been classified by Kraken2 (Wood et al. 2019. DOI: 10.1186/s13059-019-1891-0) and exports the information to a Seurat Object (Hao et al. 2021. DOI: 10.1016/j.cell.2021.04.048).
Imports:
    Biostrings,
    data.table,
    dplyr,
    parallel,
    ShortRead,
    stringr,
    tidyr
